 victori on the Eastern front . Wednesday 16.8.16 Quiet as usual , rain slight , Paid 40 Franc , 1.8.8 Thursday 17.8.16 Still rain , road veri muddi . Receiv letter parcel from home . Had a look over a fine old church in Doulieu a few day back , which was complet burnt out by the German , with the use of petroleum . Friday 18.8.16 A B Sec came here rout march this morn , appear to be get a rough time with squad drill again . Saturday 19.8.16 Rain hard dure morn . Dozen of Tommi come here direct from Somm look much the wors for their experi ; they tell some veri appal tale of the Slaughter
